    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// Transaction埋点</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">Transaction</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">t</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Cat</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">newTransaction</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;Service&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&#34;createOrder&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">try</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">Order</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">order</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">orderService</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">create</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">Cat</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">logEvent</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;OrderCreated&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">String</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">valueOf</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">order</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">getId</span><span class="p">()));</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">t</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">setStatus</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Transaction</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">SUCCESS</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">catch</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Exception</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">Cat</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">logError</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">t</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">setStatus</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">finally</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">t</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">complete</span><span class="p">();</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 简化方式（使用AOP或注解）</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nd">@CatTransaction</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">type</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&#34;Service&#34;</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">name</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="s">&#34;createOrder&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Order</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">createOrder</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">OrderRequest</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">orderService</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">create</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="实际应用中的决策与权衡">实际应用中的决策与权衡</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>场景</th>
          <th>埋点策略</th>
          <th>原因</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>核心接口</td>
          <td>全量Transaction</td>
          <td>精确监控RT和成功率</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>高频调用</td>
          <td>采样（1%）</td>
          <td>减少性能开销</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>异常处理</td>
          <td>必报Event</td>
          <td>不遗漏错误</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>业务指标</td>
          <td>Metric聚合</td>
          <td>实时大盘</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1埋点过多影响性能">问题1：埋点过多影响性能</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：每个埋点都有创建和序列化开销
<strong>解决</strong>：核心链路全量、非核心采样、异步上报</p>]]></description></item><item><title>统计系统</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="统计系统">统计系统</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：统计系统通过埋点采集数据，通过实时链路（Flink/Kafka）提供秒级指标，通过离线链路（Hive/Spark）提供T+1精确报表，通过数据仓库分层实现数据治理。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="统计系统通过埋点采集实时离线双链路计算支撑业务指标和运营决策">统计系统通过埋点采集、实时+离线双链路计算，支撑业务指标和运营决策</h2>
<h3 id="数据采集埋点设计">数据采集：埋点设计</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>埋点类型</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>示例</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>页面曝光</td>
          <td>用户进入页面</td>
          <td>page_view</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>点击事件</td>
          <td>用户点击按钮</td>
          <td>button_click</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>业务事件</td>
          <td>核心业务流程</td>
          <td>order_create, payment_success</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>性能事件</td>
          <td>接口耗时、错误</td>
          <td>api_latency, error_log</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
