    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">埋点数据格式：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">{
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  &#34;event&#34;: &#34;order_create&#34;,
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  &#34;timestamp&#34;: 1714400000000,
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  &#34;user_id&#34;: &#34;10001&#34;,
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  &#34;device_id&#34;: &#34;abc123&#34;,
