</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">}</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="实时-vs-离线计算">实时 vs 离线计算</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>维度</th>
          <th>实时计算</th>
          <th>离线计算</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>延迟</td>
          <td>秒级~分钟级</td>
          <td>小时级~天级</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>准确性</td>
          <td>近似（可能丢数据）</td>
          <td>精确（全量数据）</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>技术栈</td>
          <td>Flink + Kafka</td>
          <td>Spark + Hive</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>用途</td>
          <td>实时监控、大屏</td>
          <td>财务报表、对账</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>存储</td>
          <td>Redis / Druid</td>
          <td>Hive / ClickHouse</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="数据仓库分层">数据仓库分层</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
